    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the overall body of evidence is sufficient to support the intended use. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed, and the majority of factors were formally assessed. The two factors lacking formal level grading (Numerical solver error and Use error) were reviewed qualitatively and deemed to present no material risk to the acceptance decision. The team concluded that the model is fit for purpose for predicting absolute hemolysis levels under VAD operating conditions.",
